### Mortality Rate

//let path = "/Users/hongkeesul/Dropbox/Research_obsidian/Research";//absolute path to your vault

var data = [
 {name:"Mortality Rate", x:  pg.Date.values.map(x => moment(x.toString()).format("YYYY-MM-DD")),y: data2.values},
];
